                    </p>
                    <p class="about-text">
                        What began as a startup with a handful of dedicated individuals has grown into a comprehensive healthcare information management system trusted by hundreds of medical facilities across the country. Today, HealthRec continues to innovate at the intersection of healthcare and technology, making patient care more efficient, accurate, and accessible.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

